## 12. DECISION FRAMEWORK

### **Master Issuer/Series Programme Makes Sense IF:**

✅ Planning 3+ issuances within 24 months  
✅ Consistent collateral type (or definable variants)  
✅ Desire to build programme brand/investor franchise  
✅ Operational infrastructure for multi-series management  
✅ Committed to medium-term securitization funding (not just opportunistic)

### **Stick with Traditional Shelf IF:**

❌ Issuance frequency uncertain  
❌ Material collateral type variation deal-to-deal  
❌ Opportunistic execution only (test market, then decide)  
❌ Limited internal resources for programme management  
❌ Prefer flexibility to change structure/terms each deal

### **Your Client:**

Based on their message (5 deals planned, £1.15bn, seeking systematic solutions):

**STRONG CANDIDATE** for Master Issuer Programme

